data.description: Exceptionally beautiful 4bed/2.5 bath home that is nestled in the coveted Arrowhead Ranch community. It has been meticulously maintained with updated light fixtures and new exterior paint. You'll find a grand entryway that leads into the living and dining rooms. Granite countertops, gas stove and refreshed cabinets are some highlights of the spacious kitchen. Family room has a lot of natural light and plenty of room for the family. Step outside to the patio where you'll find a wonderful space for outdoor living and entertaining. New built in bbq with two large shade trees will keep you grilling and comfortable year round. Upstairs 3 bdrms and master with double sinks soaking tub, new toilet, step in shower and walk in closet. Close to shopping, food and entertainment. Deer valley schools.
